* {{cite book |last = Loo, C. T. et compagnie Paris American Art Association  |first =  |year = 1915 |title = Catalogue of Antique Chinese Porcelains Pottery, Carved Jades, Agates and Rugs and Carpets Belonging to Loo & Cie., (Société Chinoise Léyer) ... The Entire Collection to Be Sold at Unrestricted Public Sale at the American Art Galleries ... On [May 5th and 6th, 1915] |publisher = American Art Assoc.| location = New York|url=http://catalog.hathitrust.org/api/volumes/oclc/40503504.html|isbn = |ref =}} Hathi Trust.
